MinIPC

Build from bottom to up

1. Messaging Patterns
structured methods for exchanging messages
Shared Memory Side:
Store, Ring Buffer, Queues
Message Passing Side:
store, pubsub, reqresp
Dispenser (FIFO, LIFO)
RPC


2. Messaging Engine 
encoding, decoding, processing
Shared Memory Side: locks, semaphores
Message Passing Side: 
blocking/nonblocking,
sync/async,
XDR,
flow control

3. Transport Layer
low level message transmission
Shared Memory, Pipes, Sockets